task.summary: Gradle: svg -> png generation added to every build
gitignore update (to omit passwords from gradle.properties)
bugfix: for multi-fuel refuelling correcting display in "last costs"
bugfix: changed tyre structure on axle from list to map in order to allow simplexml framework to work with null objects (i.e. no tyre installed on axle)
bugfix: ordering of the tyres in the scheme bugfix: new scheme doesn't start from the previous scheme feature: support more than 4 tyres on the axle in the TyreChangeSchemeGraphics

bugfix: if tyre is selected in the scheme, stats are not refreshed bugfix: if adding or deleting tyres the cost of the entry isn't automatically updated bugfix: can't delete the tyre in the latest entry directly from the scheme (which should be possible)
bugfix: typo in maintenance bugfix: insurance payment activity crash
feature: garage backup to compressed XML file
